label: spam
subject: advice on dealing
body: Γλανὶς, a fresh-water fish, Silurus glanis, _Strack_, 9, 38, 40, 219; conjoined spawn, 155: two species, the greater and the smaller, the male watches the spawn, _ib._; size of the ova, 156; diseases, 219; unfit to eat when in spawn, the female better than the male, 229; the male watches the young, breaks the hook with its teeth, 256.
